data.description: What a way to welcome Spring in your sprawling, well maintained ranch style home.  This lovely home features a large Living Room with lots of natural light and new carpeting, as well as a spacious eat-in kitchen with a built-in snack/coffee bar and new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout.  Enjoy the gas fireplace in your Family Room, directly off the kitchen before stepping out to the patio in your huge fenced in backyard with the nice shed for additional storage.  You also have the finished basement to use for more living space with an option for a 4th bedroom or work-out room, and tons of storage.  All 3 bedrooms have plenty of closet space with additional pantry and closets in the foyer, mud area, and family room.  No need to look any further, it's the perfect neighborhood and home for your family!
